	(_make_dico_port): Rewrite using scm_new_port_table_entry.
	(_dico_port_seek): Change prototype. Second arg is scm_t_off.
	(mod_init)[GUILE_DEBUG_MACROS]: Protect the use of
	SCM_DEVAL_P and friends.
